race.comment: The betting moves will be instructive. Despite awkward barriers, debutants may hold the key. GANGSTER PARADISE (3) appeals on debut. He's a nicely bred gelding by Pride Of Dubai from the stakes-winner Backflash and has had five hitouts leading into this. Has a wide gate to overcome, but this is a winnable race. TITANIC (10) debuts and won a recent trial at Avoca. The gate is against, but he also profiles well. LIM'S TEIDE (7) is another debutant who appeals at first blush. Has been well-educated, but he also needs some luck in the run. BRAZEN FLING (12) and STRUM (9) rate best of the raced division, and deserve consideration at longer odds.
